These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
House: art-deco, wooden
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, egyptian
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, yellow
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, scientific
1. the art-deco house is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the pakistani is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| House       | wooden       | art-deco |
| Nationality         | egyptian | pakistani  |
| Color       | yellow    | fuchsia    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific       | fantasy      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: corn, cauliflower
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, tulip
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, train
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, azure
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Food      | cauliflower     | corn |
| Flower           | azalea | tulip      |
| Transport   | train  | boat      |
| Color         | mauve | azure     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, balloon-flower
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, police-officer
City: marseilles, liverpool
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, rat
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the person who growsorchid is the owner of the rat##1
3. the analyst is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Flower      | orchid | balloon-flower  |
| Job          | analyst    | police-officer   |
| City   | liverpool  | marseilles   |
| Pet     | rat     | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, swimming
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, black
2 different pets are kept: fish, turtle
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, july
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Sport      | water-polo       | swimming |
| Color          | black         | lavender    |
| Pet           | turtle | fish    |
| Birthday   | august           | july   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-5::.
City: hannover, san-francisco
There are 2 different favourite colors: yellow, coral
2 different pets are kept: lizard, pony
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, siglo
1. the person who likes yellow is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| City         | hannover | san-francisco   |
| Color   | yellow | coral       |
| Pet         | lizard   | pony |
| Cigar     | siglo    | swisher     |

