There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, cola
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, ebony
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the fan of soul##1
2. the person who likes ebony is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person who likes amber is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |      2       |
| Music-Genre         | d&b            | soul  |
| Beverage           | cola | soy-milk |
| Color   | amber           | ebony       |
| Sport     | cycling            | lacrosse        |

