.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, august
There 2 different types of food: corn, radish
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, azalea
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, puzzles
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person eating corn##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Birthday           | august | january     |
| Food   | corn          | radish |
| Flower           | bellflower          | azalea    |
| Hobby     | puzzles            | skydiving       |

 